just when you think everything is fine, your whole world is shattered and you see that nothing is what it really seems to be. as time progresses, there is more evil being displayed in the already impure hearts of the masses. trust is a sacred object more holy than the manuscript that the devout follow. individuals destroy the trust that they have earned, leaving a constant select few, and abandon them. desperate for a new life to build, the broken man is slowly being strangled and their hope for survival is being eradicated, until a day comes when they collapse and realize that their striving was futile because they could not change their fate. they would always be abused and broken no matter the situation because of who they are inside themselves. time after time their trust is broken and time after time the hearts of the evil fill with more of their deadly venom and begin to subconsciously or consciously look for a new victim to destroy.

i just got home from the moorestown mall... i drove there and scared my mom. i got a few things but i would have bought more if i had more money. ummm i sucked so bad in my game today, we lost 3-0 to cinnaminson... oh well... umm i dont know what else...

ive been feelin bad all day... i passed out last night trying to read the last chapter my history test was on... and i missed my friends call even though i promised her id stay up... i realized it when i woke up at 3 in the morning and saw the missed call thing on the screen. i was so pissed... then i tried to study for my test and i fell asleep like right after i finished reading, so i didnt study at all. i had the test last block and im pretty sure i did really bad on it... oh well. my chem teacher showed me, kyle, and jimmy how to make a stink bomb with iron, sulfur and hydrochloric acid. my lab table was in the middle of the room and when the shit started smellin everyone either left the room or stayed along the walls. that was like the only fun part of my day. ceramics should be pretty fun since im makin this kick ass pot with some mudvayne shit carved into it. i dont know what im gonna make when im finished that...

state of emergency.... my game was cancelled. =D i was so happy. we beat delran the other day like 20 seconds into overtime 1-0. that was good... but my home life fuckin sucks... im leavin it at that.

i went to the football game friday night... i was walkin around with mike and joe most of the time... we won like 55-18 i think it was over new egypt. but they suck ass anyway. yesterday i had to work then i went bowlin with shaniqua, jason, holly, carl, andrew and like 2 other girls (i cant remember their names). my name was "teabagged." that was pretty fun... but now i have to work today... lucky me... =\

i finally got my hat and shirt in the mail today. they fuckin rock. i had a scrimmage today and won 1-0. i took a shot to my titty and it hurt my nipple... oh well... school tomorrow... fuckin summer went by too fast... =(

just a lot of shit has been botherin me lately. i dont know if any of its my fault though... i dont know where anything is headed. i dont know what the hell im doing. i dont know what the fuck i should be doing. i dont know a goddamn thing. nothing makes sense to me anymore. there are a few times when i can escape how i feel but it dont last for long. and then im back here wondering what the hell i fucked up this time. i wish i could know and understand what goes on but im never that damn lucky. i feel lost and trapped within a spiral where some things change but then im thrown right back around to where i started. maybe its just me i dont know. i was working today and i hadnt felt that tired in such a long time. i got a lot of sleep last night but it didnt do any good. i think that all the shit thats bothering me is starting to wear me down. i just really wish i knew what it is thats bothering me so much and what i could do to get over it. i dont know how much more i can take being like this...
